reviewText:
Great game, has awesome graphics and its pretty scary imo. 7/10

Things that could be better:
-Footstep sounds are not synced (if ur walking really slow with with ur analog stick it still performs the sound as if u were walking normally);
-The achievements were implemented with the number of times u save the game and not the location (if u save the game tons of times you will win all the achievements except the chapter ones);
-Deaths and other animations could be better.

But overall a really solid game :)
